      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MUNNY THE MUNSTER (2) raced parked and cruised home when resuming in Victoria two back before fighting strongly to go under by just a head in the NSW Derby last start. That was his third Group 1 placing so he is a young talent on the way up. The good draw should see him hard to stop. THE PREACHER (4) looks to have come back in good order and should be fitter for his resuming second from this barrier at Kilmore. KICKING HORSE (9) draws for a trail and was good when resuming with a placing in Brisbane so could measure up. ICONIC IMAGE (5) has trialled since the fresh effort so should have come on and races well second-up so can improve.",
